						<div class="postbody">I don't have the tools to build a custom cartridge, let alone test it on one.  That's why it's at $a0 instead of $80 or $00.  It's funny how Nintendo never placed SRAM in the most optimal places.<br /><br />It only takes approximately 30 lines because once it hits the max amount of DMA size, it ignores everything after it.</div>

