				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Sure. With 16-bit M/X, the effects of fast B bank seem to be very approximately equal to fast K bank. And with a standard LoROM cart, you can even use cart RAM with fast timings.<br /><br />But with 8-bit M/X, the benefits of fast B bank are only roughly 1/3 ish of fast K bank. It's not clear whether that difference is big enough to matter.</div>

